OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells.
OL,6,FSoon becoming cloudier through the
OL,7,Fmorning with outbreaks of rain.
OL,8,FBrighter spells and the odd shower for
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Winds strong at times,
OL,10,Fespecially near the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy through the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain, which may be heavy at times.
OL,15,FWinds strong at times, especially near
OL,16,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
