OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA mixed day of bright or sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers, which may be heavy
OL,7,Fat times. Strong southwesterly winds
OL,8,Fwhich may reach gale force before
OL,9,Feasing in the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and showers on Monday. Dry
OL,13,Fstart with rain later on Tuesday.
OL,14,FMostly cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fon Wednesday. Winds light Monday then
OL,16,Fbreezy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
